== 製作 ==

[[File:Chris_Columbus.jpg|thumb]]擔任電影的導演及製片人。]]

2004年6月，[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]收購了該書的{{link-en|電影版權|Film rights}}<ref>{{cite news |first=Claude |last=Brodesser |title='Lightning Thief' strikes Maverick |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117906944.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5gmmoXAco?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117906944.html?categoryid=1236 |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] |date=2004-06-23 |archivedate=2009-05-15 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2007年6月，[[克里斯·哥倫布|克里斯·哥倫布]]受聘擔任導演<ref name="struck">{{cite news |first=Peter |last=Gilstrap |title=Columbus struck by 'Lightning' |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117963285.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5gmn2hgI8?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117963285.html?categoryid=13 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2007-04-17 |archivedate=2009-05-15 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。拍攝於2009年4月在[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]開始<ref name="bulk">{{cite news |first = Tatiana |last = Siegel |title = Fox 2000 bulks up 'Percy Jackson' |url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118001666.html |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090430110528/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118001666.html?categoryid=1238&cs=1 |work =[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] |date = 2009-03-25 |archivedate = 2009-04-30 |accessdate = 2009-05-15 }}</ref>。電影的一部分於田納西州[[納許維爾|納許維爾]]的[[帕德嫩神廟_(納許維爾)|帕德嫩神廟]]取景，該神廟為原址[[雅典|雅典]][[帕德嫩神廟|帕德嫩神廟]]的1比1複製品<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.wsmv.com/community/19638346/detail.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5hnExocye?url=http://www.wsmv.com/community/19638346/detail.html |title=Portions Of Movie To Be Shot At Parthenon |accessdate=2009-06-25 |archivedate=2009-06-25 |date=2009-06-02 |publisher={{link-en|WSMV-TV|WSMV-TV}} |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。7月25日上午，《波西傑克森：神火之賊》於不列顛哥倫比亞的[[米遜_(卑詩省)|米遜]]殺青{{citation needed|date=2017年4月}}。劇組於8月的第1個星期在紐約市[[布魯克林區|布魯克林區]]進行其他外景拍攝{{citation needed|date=2017年4月}}。[[數碼中間片|數碼中間片]]作業於2009年11月在舊金山開始<ref>{{cite news |title=Goldblatt, Deakins follow similar path |first=Peter |last=Caranicas |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118010170.html |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] |date=2009-10-20 |accessdate=2009-12-24 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5mFe9rr24?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118010170.html?categoryid=3683 |archivedate=2009-12-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。配樂工作由[[克里斯托弗·贝克|克里斯多夫·貝克]]負責<ref>{{cite news |title=New trailer for Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief hits... |first=Harry |last=Knowles |url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/43141 |work={{link-en|Ain't It Cool News|Ain't It Cool News}} |date=2009-11-20 |accessdate=2009-12-24 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5mFffCexA?url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/43141 |archivedate=2009-12-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

== 發行 ==

《波西傑克森：神火之賊》於2010年2月4日在[[紐約市|紐約市]]的AMC林肯廣場13號舉行[[首映|首映]]禮<ref>{{cite news |title = “Percy Jackson and The Olympians: The Lightning Thief”: The Premiere |url = http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2010/02/05/percy-jackson-and-the-olympians-the-lightning-thief-the-premiere/ |work = [[華爾街日報|The Wall Street Journal]] |date = 2010-02-05 |accessdate = 2010-02-05 |archive-date = 2017-05-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170520024617/https://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2010/02/05/percy-jackson-and-the-olympians-the-lightning-thief-the-premiere/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 家庭媒體 ===

該片的[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]<ref name="ReferenceA" />及[[藍光光碟|藍光]]<ref name="ReferenceB" />版本於2010年6月29日發布。《波西傑克森：神火之賊》於首週收入13,985,047美元，名列DVD銷售圖表的頂端<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.the-numbers.com/dvd/charts/weekly/2010/20100704.php|title=US DVD Sales Chart for Week Ending Jul 4, 2010|work=[[The_Numbers_(網站)|The Numbers]]|date=2010-07-04|accessdate=2010-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715120636/http://www.the-numbers.com/dvd/charts/weekly/2010/20100704.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2011年10月，電影已售出2,087,368張DVD，獲益總額超過3,700萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2010/PJALT-DVD.php|title=Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief - DVD Sales|work=The Numbers|access-date=2017-04-01|archive-date=2013-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110002017/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2010/PJALT-DVD.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 迴響 ==

=== 評價 ===

[[File:Logan_Lerman_at_the_Apple_Store_Soho_in_New_York_City,_July_29,_2013.jpg|thumb]]的演出給予好評。]]

電影收穫普遍的混合評價。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的143篇專業影評文章，其中70篇給予該片「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為49%，平均得分5.3分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/0814255/|title=Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief (2010)|work=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=Flixster|accessdate=2014-02-26|archive-date=2013-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130127234548/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/0814255/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而基於另一影評匯總網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的31篇評論文章，其中9篇予以好評，4篇差評，18篇褒貶不一，平均分為47（滿分100），代表「混合或中等評價」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/percy-jackson-the-olympians-the-lightning-thief|title=Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=CBS Interactive Inc.|accessdate=2014-02-26|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103000246/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/percy-jackson-the-olympians-the-lightning-thief|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

該片獲得部分影評人的良好反響。《[[休士頓紀事報|休士頓紀事報]]》的艾米·比安寇利給予電影3顆星（滿分4顆）的評價，寫道「導演[[克里斯·哥倫布|克里斯·哥倫布]]以急促的節奏匯集現代和神話領域，以及有趣的俏皮感覺彌補了電影的瘋狂片段。這是繼《[[哈利波特：消失的密室_(電影)|哈利波特：消失的密室]]》以來最令人愉快的成就。」<ref>{{cite web | last = Biancolli | first = Amy | title = Percy Jackson & the Olympians:The Lightning Thief Percy Jackson rules the world with goofy charm | work = [[休士頓紀事報|Houston Chronicle]] | url = http://www.chron.com/entertainment/movies/article/Percy-Jackson-the-Olympians-The-Lightning-Thief-1714807.php | accessdate = 2010-02-11 | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923005008/https://www.chron.com/entertainment/movies/article/Percy-Jackson-the-Olympians-The-Lightning-Thief-1714807.php | dead-url = no }}{{Rating|3|4}}</ref>。《[[紐約每日新聞|紐約每日新聞]]》的伊莉莎白·韋茲曼稱「你甚至不必熟悉[[雷克·萊爾頓|雷克·萊爾頓]]流行奇幻系列中的首部作品，便可享受克里斯·哥倫布充滿活力的改編。」<ref>{{cite web | last = Weitzman | first = Elizabeth | title = 'Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief': Growing up can be a real jolt | work = [[紐約每日新聞|New York Daily News]] | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/percy-jackson-olympians-lightning-thief-growing-real-jolt-article-1.174524 | accessdate = 2010-02-11 | archive-date = 2018-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180304061328/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/percy-jackson-olympians-lightning-thief-growing-real-jolt-article-1.174524 | dead-url = no }}{{Rating|3|5}}</ref>。

此外，《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的{{link-en|肯尼斯·圖藍|Kenneth Turan}}給予負評，描述電影為「標準的好萊塢產品……沒冒險且無趣。」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-et-percy12-2010feb12,0,3353954.story |title=Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief Review |work=Los Angeles Times | first=Kenneth | last=Turan | accessdate =2010-02-12}}</ref>。《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的影評人認為「該片遭受些微過度嚴肅之苦。這不僅是較原著少去許多有趣之處。電影本身也少去許多樂趣。」<ref>{{cite news|first=Michael |last=O'Sullivan |title=Critic Review for Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/gog/movies/percy-jackson-and-the-olympians-the-lightning-thief,1158925/critic-review.html#reviewNum1 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113062304/http://www.washingtonpost.com/gog/movies/percy-jackson-and-the-olympians-the-lightning-thief%2C1158925/critic-review.html |work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]] |accessdate=2010-02-12 |archivedate=2012-11-13 |deadurl=yes }}{{Rating|2|4}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===

在美國，電影於2010年2月12日在3,356家劇院開始發行；於其首映週末進帳31,236,067美元<ref name="bom" />，超越當週第三的《{{link-en|狼嚎再起|The Wolfman (2010 film)}}》（31,479,235美元），但落後《[[情人節快樂|情人節快樂]]》（56,260,707美元）排名第二<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=daily&id=valentinesday.htm |title=Valentine's Day (2010) - Daily Box Office Results - Box Office Mojo<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2017-04-01 |archive-date=2010-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100221073150/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=daily&id=valentinesday.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該片有著強而有力的首映週末成績，為奇幻片中，非《[[哈利波特系列電影|哈利波特]]》、《[[納尼亞傳奇系列電影|納尼亞傳奇]]》及《[[魔戒電影三部曲|魔戒]]》系列作品的最高首週末票房數字<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2681&p=.htm |title=Weekend Report: 'Valentine's Day' Massacres Presidents' Day Record |work=Box Office Mojo |date=2010-02-16 |accessdate=2010-05-07 |archive-date=2010-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100514091658/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2681&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2010年9月14日，美國的總票房收入為88,768,303美元，其他地區137,728,906美元，全球共計226,497,209美元<ref name="bom" />。

