== 電子遊戲 ==

以電影為基礎改編，並由[[動視|動視]]開發的[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]在2010年2月11日透過[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]發布<ref name="Video game">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/ds/rpg/percyjacksontheolympiansthelightningthief/index.html |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100722030906/http://www.gamespot.com/ds/rpg/percyjacksontheolympiansthelightningthief/index.html |title=Percy Jackson and the Olympians: The Lightning Thief for DS - Percy Jackson and the Olympians: The Lightning Thief Nintendo DS - Percy Jackson and the Olympians: The Lightning Thief DS Game |publisher=Gamespot.com |date= |archivedate = 2010-07-22|accessdate=2010-05-07}}</ref>。[[GameZone|GameZone]]的麥克·斯畢利塔給予其6分（滿分10分）的評價，表示「波西·傑克森也許在電影連線遊戲中不會引起轟動，但回合制戰鬥的粉絲可能會在這個遊戲中找到一些挽回的特點。」<ref name="gamezone">{{cite web|url=http://nds.gamezone.com/gzreviews/r39716.htm|title=Percy Jackson & The Olympians: The Lightning Thief Review |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100305065405/http://nds.gamezone.com/gzreviews/r39716.htm |last=Splechta|first=Michael|publisher=[[GameZone|GameZone]].com|archivedate = 2010-03-05|accessdate=2010-02-26}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，根據該網站收集的6篇評論文章，其中1篇予以好評，2篇差評，3篇褒貶不一，平均分為56（滿分100），代表「混合或中等評價」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/ds/percy-jackson-and-the-olympians-the-lightning-thief |title=Percy Jackson and the Olympians: The Lightning Thief Reviews, Ratings, Credits, and More at Metacritic |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2013-07-18 |archive-date=2021-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403215812/https://www.metacritic.com/game/ds/percy-jackson-and-the-olympians-the-lightning-thief |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

